Big Brother Naija, BBNaija, Lockdown housemate, Vee, has told Neo that he has the potential of a good husband. She stated this while dining with Neo last night. Vee, who had last Sunday told Neo that she is no longer interested in having a romantic relationship with him, also said that the 26-year-old housemate needed just one or two things to look out for. Vee to Neo: “I know your mum is looking at how strict I am with you. “You have the potential of a very good husband. “Just one or two things you need to look for.” Meanwhile, Neo had begged Vee for reconciliation and romantic relationship. Neo to Vee: “I know what I want, and what I want is that girl who asked me to sleep on her bed that night.”